> I always list every possible thing wrong with a vehicle before I sell it.
> Make a list, and give it to prospective buyers.  I've never had one come
> back due to "Hey, the whatzitdohickey was broken and you didn't tell me
> about it!" Syndrome.
>
> Granted, I sometimes lose a few bucks on the selling price, but it's a small
